title: Enhancing Metaverse Integration: My Neighbor Alice Joins The Board of Directors of OMA3
description: Stockholm, Sweden, June 12th, 2023, Chainwire Riccardo Sibani, Chief Product Officer at My Neighbor Alice, represents the company on the OMA3 Board and contributes to developing a more interconnected metaverse. My Neighbor Alice, the fully-decentralized open-world game, is proud to announce that its Chief Product Officer (CPO) has joined the board of directors of OMA3 [...]
